---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Episodes
hero_image: /assets/img/episodes.png
hero_alt: "A herd on the move"
---

<div class="page-content">

  <p>
    Each episode is a working conversation about long-term change in agri-food—how people adapt, coordinate, and lead together under real-world constraints.
  </p>

  <p class="small">
    Want updates automatically? <a href="/listen/">Listen and follow the show</a>.
  </p>

  {% if collections.episodes and collections.episodes.length %}
    <ul class="episode-list">
      {% for ep in collections.episodes | reverse %}
        <li class="episode-item">
          {% if ep.data.image %}
            <a class="episode-thumb" href="{{ ep.url }}">
              <img
                src="{{ ep.data.image }}"
                alt="{{ ep.data.imageAlt or ep.data.title }}"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </a>
          {% endif %}

          <div class="episode-info">
            <a class="episode-title" href="{{ ep.url }}">{{ ep.data.title }}</a>

            <div class="small" style="margin-top: 4px;">
              {% if ep.data.episodeNumber %}Ep {{ ep.data.episodeNumber }} · {% endif %}
              {% if ep.date %}{{ ep.date | postDate }}{% endif %}
            </div>

            {% if ep.data.summary %}
              <div class="small" style="margin-top: 8px;">
                {{ ep.data.summary }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p class="small">
      Episodes will appear here as they go live. In the meantime, you can listen on the web or follow the show via <a href="/listen/">Listen</a>.
    </p>
  {% endif %}

</div>
